Map of the road:

We can move giving commands [n s w e ] that correspond with the polar coordinates
-------> 5
|        |
|        |
2 < ---> 1 <---> 3
^        |
|        |
|------- 4

Directions that we can move :
From 1:
    In all directions
From 2:
    To 5
From 3:
    To 1
From 4:
    To 1
    To 2
From 5:
    To 1
    To 2